## Decision
Use JWT tokens with refresh tokens.

## Consequences
- Pros: Stateless, scalable
- Cons: Token size, revocation complexity
```

## Documentation Standards

### Writing Style
- Active voice
- Present tense
- Short sentences
- Clear examples
- No jargon without explanation

### Code Examples
