- GET request with password in URL â†’ STOP
- Plain text password storage â†’ STOP
- Auth tokens in localStorage â†’ STOP
- Missing HTTPS on auth â†’ STOP
- SQL injection vulnerability â†’ STOP
- XSS vulnerability â†’ STOP
- Exposed API keys in code â†’ STOP

## Security Protocol

### Initial Assessment
```bash
