   â†“
4. COLLECT ALL RESULTS from parallel validators
   â†“
5. If ANY validator fails:
   â”Œâ”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”
   â”‚ MANDATORY FIX CYCLE:            â”‚
   â”‚ â€¢ Gather ALL reported issues    â”‚
   â”‚ â€¢ Create Fix Tasks for each     â”‚
   â”‚ â€¢ Implement ALL fixes           â”‚
   â”‚ â€¢ Re-run Integration Step       â”‚
   â”‚ â€¢ Re-run ALL Validation Steps   â”‚
   â”‚ â€¢ REPEAT until 100% PASS        â”‚
   â”‚                                 â”‚
   â”‚ NEVER SKIP THIS CYCLE!          â”‚
   â”‚ NEVER PROCEED WITH FAILURES!    â”‚
   â””â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”˜
